OL,3,COnly 17% of Jersey directors feel
OL,4,Coptimistic about the economy
OL,6,FJersey business leaders say they are
OL,7,Ffeeling pessimistic about the state of
OL,8,Fthe island's economy and are calling
OL,9,Fon the government to cut public
OL,10,Fspending to give it a boost.
OL,12,FIn the Institute of Directors (IoD)
OL,13,F2025 survey, more than half of
OL,14,Fdirectors said they were optimistic
OL,15,Fabout their own organisation's
OL,16,Foutlook, but 63% were pessimistic
OL,17,Fabout the island's economy.
