OL,3,COnly 17% of Jersey directors feel
OL,4,Coptimistic about the economy
OL,6,FThe Jersey Institute of Directors
OL,7,Fcompared its results to those of
OL,8,FGuernsey and the UK using the Net
OL,9,FConfidence Index.
OL,11,FThis measures overall optimism by
OL,12,Fsubtracting pessimists from optimists
OL,13,Fin surveys, revealing sentiment about
OL,14,Fpersonal finances or the economy, with
OL,15,Fpositive scores indicating more
OL,16,Fconfidence.
OL,18,FIn the Net Confidence Index, it was
OL,19,F-46 for the economy in Jersey,
OL,20,Fcompared to -12 in Guernsey, and -66
OL,21,Fin the UK.
