OL,3,COnly 17% of Jersey directors feel
OL,4,Coptimistic about the economy
OL,6,FIt indicates that despite Guernsey's
OL,7,Fpoor financial situation, business
OL,8,Fleaders there have more confidence
OL,9,Fthan they do in Jersey.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the IoD said: "The
OL,12,Freport serves as a wake-up call for
OL,13,Fpolicymakers ahead of the 2026
OL,14,Felections.
OL,16,F"Businesses are urging a clear reset
OL,17,Fof public sector spending, certainty
OL,18,Fover investment plans, and reforms to
OL,19,Freduce regulatory overhead. restoring
OL,20,Ffiscal reserves remains a priority."
