OL,3,COnly 17% of Jersey directors feel
OL,4,Coptimistic about the economy
OL,6,FAlex Ruddy, IoD Jersey Chair,
OL,7,Fcommented: "The results of our third
OL,8,Fsurvey highlight a clear confidence
OL,9,Fgap between the outlook for individual
OL,10,Fbusinesses and the wider Jersey
OL,11,Feconomy.
OL,13,F"While many organisations remain
OL,14,Fresilient, the persistent pessimism
OL,15,Fabout the broader economic environment
OL,16,Fis a warning sign."
