OL,6,FShe added: "Ahead of the 2026
OL,7,Felections, we urge policymakers to
OL,8,Fprioritise fiscal discipline, provide
OL,9,Fcertainty on investment plans, and
OL,10,Freduce regulatory burdens.
OL,12,F"Jersey's future competitiveness
OL,13,Fdepends on decisive action now. IoD
OL,14,FJersey will continue to engage with
OL,15,Fgovernment and stakeholders to ensure
OL,16,Fthat the voice of business is heard in
OL,17,Fshaping the island's economic future."
